HEADWORD: Consecute
<hw>Con"se*cute</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To follow
closely; to endeavor to overtake; to pursue.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bp. Burnet.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

